== 人口 ==
洛厄尔拥有大量的[[柬埔寨|柬埔寨]]人，柬埔寨人口比例是美国最高的，达到10.37％<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.epodunk.com/ancestry/Cambodian.html |title=Cambodian ancestry by city - ePodunk |access-date=2013-11-01 |archive-date=2019-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191112062038/http://epodunk.com/ancestry/Cambodian.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。柬埔寨人总数居美国第二，仅次于[[加州|加州]][[长滩|长滩]]。估计洛厄尔及周边范围内柬埔寨人总数有25,000-35,000。<ref name=Khmer>[http://khmerization.blogspot.com/2009/04/cambodian-consulate-opens-in-lowell.html "Cambodian Consulate Opens in Lowell"] {{Wayback|url=http://khmerization.blogspot.com/2009/04/cambodian-consulate-opens-in-lowell.html |date=20210408175900 }}, Khmerization, 27 Apr 2009, accessed 26 Oct 2010</ref>为此柬埔寨政府也于2009年在洛厄尔开辟了在美国的第三个领事办公室，另外两个分别在加州长滩和[[西雅图|西雅图]]。

除了柬埔寨人以外，洛厄尔还拥有大量的[[越南|越南]]，[[老挝|老挝]]，[[泰国|泰国]]等东南亚人口。亚裔总数占人口比例的20.2%。<ref>[http://factfinder2.census.gov/faces/tableservices/jsf/pages/productview.xhtml?src=bkmk 2010年人口普查] {{Wayback|url=http://factfinder2.census.gov/faces/tableservices/jsf/pages/productview.xhtml?src=bkmk |date=20140815134909 }}"</ref>

